sub_title: I believe that the Dutch food scene is boring and I am here to do something about it.
summary:
I create new flavours and launch them to market, based on data.

I am an entrepreneur operating in the food industry and obsessed with building systems to reach optimal efficiency. Therefore, I use a scientific approach utilizing data and the latest technologies to create new flavours, identify opportunities in the market, test the market and convert them into sustainable businesses. Cheers!
